{{Otheruses|Prophet}}
The '''Third Prophet''' was the highest rank in the [[Ni'Shaw-Dak Ministry]]. The Third Prophet took all of the important decisions, aided by twelve [[Al'ma'den]]s or papal priests.<ref name="AIR">''[[Alliance Intelligence Reports]]''</ref>

The name of the rank comes from the [[Jydan Writings]] tradition: Each god was to communicate his or her teachings throughout the mouths of three prophets. For years, [[Ni'Shaw]] only had two prophets, and this led to him being forgotten. The founder of Ni'Shaw-Dak discovered the first two prophet's writings on Ni'Shaw and considered it a sign of him to become the third prophet, or Third Prophet.<ref name="AIR" />

As of [[2 ABY/Legends|2 ABY]], [[Kaltor Naklian]], founder of Ni'Shaw-Dak, retained the rank of Third Prophet while also working as a [[Scalp hunter|scalphunter]].<ref name="AIR" />

